# **Dental Chamber Management System - Project Planning**

## **1. PROJECT OVERVIEW**

A comprehensive clinic management system for dental practices with patient management, appointment scheduling, billing, inventory, and reporting capabilities.

---

## **2. USER ROLES & PERMISSIONS**

### **2.1 Role-Based Access Control**

- **Super Admin** - Full system access, user management, settings
- **Doctor** - Patient treatment, prescriptions, medical records
- **Receptionist** - Appointment scheduling, patient registration, billing
- **Accountant** - Financial management, invoices, expenses, reports
- **Inventory Manager** - Stock management, supplier coordination
- **Lab Technician** - Lab request management, result tracking
- **Patient** - Limited portal access (future phase)

---

## **3. SYSTEM MODULES**

### **3.1 Authentication & User Management Module**

- Login/Logout system
- User profile management
- Password reset/recovery
- Role assignment
- User activity logs

### **3.2 Dashboard Module**

#### **Main Dashboard**

- Today's appointments overview
- Quick stats (patients, revenue, pending bills)
- Upcoming appointments
- Recent activities
- Notifications/alerts

#### **Doctor Dashboard**

- Daily appointment schedule
- Patient queue
- Treatment reminders
- Earnings summary

#### **Reception Dashboard**

- Walk-in patient registration
- Appointment calendar view
- Payment collection interface

### **3.3 Patient Management Module**

#### **Pages:**

1. **Patient Registration Page**

   - Add new patient with demographics
   - Medical history form
   - Insurance information (optional)

2. **Patient Listing Page**

   - Search/filter patients
   - Quick view of patient history
   - Export patient list

3. **Patient Profile Page**
   - Personal information
   - Treatment history
   - Appointment history
   - Financial summary
   - Medical files gallery
   - Prescription history

### **3.4 Appointment Management Module**

#### **Pages:**

1. **Appointment Calendar**

   - Day/Week/Month view
   - Color-coded by status
   - Drag-and-drop rescheduling

2. **Book Appointment Page**

   - Select doctor, date, time
   - Patient search/selection
   - Service selection
   - Send confirmation notification

3. **Appointment Queue Page**
   - Today's appointments list
   - Check-in/status update
   - Waiting time tracking

### **3.5 Treatment & Medical Records Module**

#### **Pages:**

1. **Treatment Dashboard**

   - Active treatments list
   - Treatment workflow tracking
   - Diagnostic tools interface

2. **Treatment Form Page**

   - Diagnosis entry
   - Treatment plan creation
   - Prescription writing
   - Lab/test request generation

3. **Medical Files Page**

   - Upload X-rays/reports/images
   - File categorization
   - View/download documents
   - Before/after comparison

4. **Prescription Module**
   - Digital prescription creation
   - Medicine database
   - Template prescriptions
   - Print prescription

### **3.6 Billing & Financial Module**

#### **Pages:**

1. **Invoice Creation Page**

   - Treatment-based billing
   - Service/item selection
   - Discount application
   - Tax calculation

2. **Payment Processing Page**

   - Multiple payment methods
   - Partial payment handling
   - Receipt generation
   - Card/mobile payment integration

3. **Accounts Receivable**

   - Pending invoices list
   - Payment reminders
   - Aging report

4. **Expense Management**
   - Expense entry
   - Category management
   - Expense reports

### **3.7 Inventory Management Module**

#### **Pages:**

1. **Inventory Dashboard**

   - Stock level overview
   - Low stock alerts
   - Expiry date warnings

2. **Inventory Items Page**

   - Item listing with search
   - Add/edit items
   - Categorization (medicine, equipment, consumables)

3. **Stock Adjustment Page**
   - Add stock (purchase)
   - Use stock (treatment/consumption)
   - Transfer between locations
   - Adjustment history

### **3.8 Laboratory Management Module**

#### **Pages:**

1. **Lab Request Page**

   - Create lab requests from treatment
   - Track request status
   - Upload lab results

2. **Lab Dashboard**
   - Pending/completed requests
   - Expected delivery tracking
   - External lab coordination

### **3.9 Reporting & Analytics Module**

#### **Pages:**

1. **Financial Reports**

   - Revenue reports (daily, monthly, yearly)
   - Doctor commission reports
   - Expense vs revenue
   - Tax reports

2. **Clinical Reports**

   - Patient statistics
   - Treatment success rates
   - Doctor performance
   - Appointment analysis

3. **Inventory Reports**

   - Stock movement
   - Consumption patterns
   - Supplier performance

4. **Export/Print Center**
   - Custom report generation
   - Data export (Excel, PDF)
   - Chart visualization

### **3.10 Settings & Configuration Module**

#### **Pages:**

1. **Clinic Settings**

   - Clinic information
   - Business hours
   - Service/price list
   - Tax configuration

2. **Doctor Management**

   - Doctor profiles
   - Schedule setup
   - Commission rates
   - Leave management

3. **System Settings**
   - Email/SMS templates
   - Notification settings
   - Backup configuration
   - API keys

---

## **4. KEY FEATURES & FUNCTIONALITIES**

### **4.1 Core Features**

- **Appointment Reminders** (SMS/Email)
- **Patient Portal** (future phase)
- **Digital Prescription**
- **Medical Charting**
- **Barcode Scanning** for inventory
- **Multi-location Support** (scalable)
- **Offline Mode** for power outages

### **4.2 Business Features**

- **Insurance Claim Processing** (optional module)
- **Package/Subscription Plans** for patients
- **Referral System**
- **Marketing Campaign Integration**
- **Tele-dentistry Consultation** (video call integration)

### **4.3 Technical Features**

- **Audit Trail** for all critical actions
- **Data Backup & Recovery**
- **Role-based UI rendering**
- **Responsive Design** for tablets
- **Real-time Notifications**
- **API for third-party integration**

---

## **5. NON-FUNCTIONAL REQUIREMENTS**

### **5.1 Performance**

- Page load < 3 seconds
- Support 50+ concurrent users
- Handle 10,000+ patient records

### **5.2 Security**

- HIPAA/GDPR compliance for medical data
- Data encryption at rest and transit
- Session timeout
- Failed login attempt lockout
- Secure password policies

### **5.3 Usability**

- Intuitive navigation
- Mobile-responsive interfaces
- Keyboard shortcuts for frequent actions
- Bulk operations
- Search with filters on all listing pages

### **5.4 Reliability**

- 99.5% uptime
- Automatic backup
- Disaster recovery plan
- Data validation at all levels

---

## **6. DEVELOPMENT PHASES**

### **Phase 1: Foundation (Core Modules)**

- User authentication & roles
- Patient management
- Appointment scheduling
- Basic treatment records
- Simple billing

### **Phase 2: Enhanced Features**

- Advanced treatment workflows
- Prescription management
- Medical files upload
- Inventory management
- Lab integration

### **Phase 3: Business Intelligence**

- Advanced reporting
- Analytics dashboard
- Financial insights
- Performance metrics

### **Phase 4: Extensions**

- Patient portal
- Mobile app
- Insurance module
- Third-party integrations

---

## **7. TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE CONSIDERATIONS**

### **Frontend:**

- SPA framework (React/Vue.js)
- Component-based design
- Reusable UI components
- Charting libraries for reports

### **Backend:**

- RESTful API design
- Microservices for scalability
- Queue system for notifications
- Background jobs for reports

### **Database:**

- Index optimization for performance
- Regular maintenance jobs
- Data archiving strategy
- Read replicas for reporting

### **Infrastructure:**

- Cloud hosting (AWS/Azure)
- CDN for static assets
- Load balancer configuration
- Monitoring and alerting

---

